{"title":"docker安装teamcity","date":"2020-05-12T19:46:21.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 13, 2020","L":"05/13/2020","MM-DD":"05-13"},"link":"2020/05/13/docker-install-teamcity","tags":["docker"],"updated":"2020-05-14T04:35:38.190Z","content":"<h2 id=\"install-teamcity-server\">Install teamcity-server<a title=\"#install-teamcity-server\" href=\"#install-teamcity-server\"></a></h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull jetbrains/teamcity-server:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>使用<code>docker search teamcity-server</code>命令可以搜索</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -itd --name teamcity-server-instance -v teamcity_server:/data/teamcity_server/datadir -v /opt/teamcity/logs:/opt/teamcity/logs -p 8111:8111 jetbrains/teamcity-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull jetbrains/teamcity-agent:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -itd --name teamcity_agent -e SERVER_URL=<span class=\"string\">\"//192.168.222.133:8111\"</span> -v teamcity_agent:/data/teamcity_agent/conf jetbrains/teamcity-agent</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"docker常用命令","link":"2020/05/14/docker-command"},"next":{"title":"docker安装kafka","link":"2020/05/08/docker-install-kafka"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2020/05/13/docker-install-teamcity/","toc":[{"id":"install-teamcity-server","title":"Install teamcity-server","index":"1"}],"reward":true}